==Finnish==
===Noun===

Pimppi 

# ''(common)'' vulva (especially a little girl's)
# ''(common)'' external female genitalia including the vagina
# ''(humorous)'' cunt, pussy

External Female genitalia including the vagina. 

===Uasge notes===

Widely used, not considered obscene or vulgar, but doesn't appear in official language. Primarily ''pimppi'' is used about a little girl's vulva and vagina, but often humorously about that of an adolescent, adult, or even elderly woman. 

